Build a “Self-Updating AI App” for Nexus Modal AI under Nexus Ultra Platforms:

Create an AI-powered system that can automatically evolve, improve, and expand its own features over time without manual updates.

🧠 Core Intelligence:
- AI decision engine that analyzes user behavior, usage data, and trends
- Auto feature suggestion system (detect missing tools, user demand)
- Self-improving prompts and workflows
- Context-aware AI assistant that learns from interactions

🔄 Auto-Evolution System:
- Generate new features/modules dynamically (PDF tools, AI tools, utilities)
- Auto-update UI components based on usage patterns
- Versioning system with safe rollback
- Feature flags for gradual rollout

📊 Learning & Feedback Loop:
- Collect user feedback automatically
- Analyze retention, drop-offs, engagement
- AI optimizes UX, pricing, and features continuously

⚙️ Backend Automation:
- Node.js + Supabase/MongoDB
- AI agents for:
