- Auto API generation for new features

🤖 AI Agents System:
- Dev Agent → writes new code modules
- QA Agent → tests features automatically
- Growth Agent → improves engagement & retention
- Monetization Agent → optimizes pricing & conversions

🚀 Deployment Intelligence:
- CI/CD auto-trigger for new updates (GitHub Actions)
- Docker + Kubernetes auto-scaling
- Safe deployment pipelines with monitoring

📱 Platform:
- Android app (Material 3)
- Web SaaS dashboard
- Admin control panel for override + monitoring

💰 Monetization Evolution:
- AI adjusts pricing tiers dynamically
- Personalized offers for users
