📈 Growth Engine:
- AI generates marketing content (videos, blogs, posts)
- Auto-publishing system
- Viral loop optimization

🔐 Security & Stability:
- Sandbox testing before deployment
- Error monitoring + auto-fix suggestions
- Backup + rollback system

📦 Output:
- Full modular GitHub repo
- Self-evolving architecture
